    Executor, AsyncExecution, Shutdownable, space.arim.universal.registry.Registrable, space.arim.universal.util.concurrent.EnhancedExecutor, space.arim.universal.util.concurrent.Scheduler

    public class DefaultAsyncExecution
extends SpongeRegistrable
implements AsyncExecution, Shutdownable
    A default implementation of AsyncExecution on the Sponge platform. Uses the server's inbuilt scheduling.
